### Test Message API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. List conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get conversation with specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations/OTHER_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get messages in conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID/messages?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Mark conversation as read
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
